description:
gesserit presents:

   A Hitlist Fills Torrent ( <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9591710" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9591710</a>  ):

         Star Trek 04-18                    (1980-1982) (DCP)




        <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Star_Trek_%28comics%29#Marvel" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Star_Trek_%28comics%29#Marvel</a>


         We now return to the Big Two, but stick with the preceding HiFis genre. :)

         Disclaimer: Alas, based on a few spot checks, the quality is worse than one
                     might expect from DCP releases of books published in the 1980s.
                     Some pages seem to be fiche fills, and while better than those
                     commonly used for Golden-Age comics, they still leave a lot to
                     be desired. AFAIK, these are the best scans available, though.
